thread.title: BRIEF-Guangdong Hybribio Biotech unit signs agreement to acquire 10 pct stake in 85 pct-owned limited partnership for 500,000 yuan

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Guangdong Hybribio Biotech unit signs agreement to acquire 10 pct stake in 85 pct-owned limited partnership for 500,000 yuan

organizations.name: reuters) - guangdong hybribio biotech co ltd

text:
Jan 24(Reuters) - Guangdong Hybribio Biotech Co Ltd
* Says its unit signed an agreement to acquire 10 percent stake in a Zhengzhou-based 85 percent-owned medical technology limited partnership for 500,000 yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/2bcm6P
